    ROUTES["<b>Driving adapters — 26 FastAPI route modules (≈71 endpoints, X-API-Key)</b><br/>verification · enrollment · search · liveness · quality · voice · nfc<br/>landmarks · multi_face · comparison · puzzle · proctor · demographics · ..."]

